quran[11]{c,v,t}:
  20,88,"O yaltinani ɓe ɓanndu ngaari marn hito= huunaango, ɓe mbi'i: "Ko ko'ol woni deweteeɗo mon e deweteeɗo Muusaa on, o yejjiti [mo ɗoo]"."
  20,89,"Enee, ɓee yiaani wonan'dema ruttataako e maɓɓe konngol, ndi maranaa ɓe kadi lorra wonaa fii non [pooɗugol] nafa."
  20,90,"Gooɗii Haaruuna maakaniino ɓe ko adii: "Ko onon yo yimɓe, pellet, on njarribora kol, pellet, Joomi mooɗon ko jurmotooɗo o jokkee kam ɗoftoɗon yamiroore am nden"."
  20,91,"Ɓe mbi'i i: "Min ceerataa ko min ñiiɓuɓe e [dewal] makkol haa Muusaa ruttoo e amen"."
  20,92,"[Muusaa] maaki: "eeyma Haaruuna, nde nji'iɗaa ɓe majjii ko haɗmaa,"
  20,93,"de njokkitataa mi? Kaa a yeddii yamirooe am on?!""
  20,94,"[Haaruuna] maaki: "eeyma ɓiy neene am, wota a nanngu wahre am nde wonaa hoore am nden kadi, miin dey, mi hulu wata a wi'i: Mi seerdii hakkunde ɓiɗɓe Israa'iila ɓe, mi heɗaaki konngol maaɗa ngol"."
  20,95,"[Muusaa] maaki: "Ko hol ɗuum woni fiyaake maaɗa on an Saamiriiyu?""
  20,96,"[Saamiriiyu] wi'i: "Mi yi'ii ko ɓe yiaani ɗum, mi nokki nokkannde e batte nulaaɗo on [Jibriila] mi wernii ɗum ko nii suɗirani lam woŋkii am."
  20,97,"[Muusaa] maaki: "Yahu, pellet, no woodanmaa ka ngurndam nde wowlataa wanaa meemondiral, pellet, no woodanmaa kadi Fodoore a lunndataako nde, ndaarii fa'ade e dewteeɗo maa, on mo ñalluɗaa ufinaade e hoore mun, mi woondii mi sumat mo refti mi ƴaroo mo ka maayo e ƴaragol"."
  20,98,"Pellet, deweteeɗo mon On ko Alla, On Mo Deweteeɗo alaa si wanaa Kaŋko, Ganndal makko Yaajanii kala hu'unde."